thread.title: Marian Robinson
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Marian Robinson

author: Marian Robinson
title: Marian Robinson
text: Tom Roberts was a skilled practioner and a wonderful support to work with recently in the sale of our property. Tom's working knowledge was well researched and he was able to combine his extended local intelligence, excellent communication skills and superior emotional intelligence to deliver terrific results on the day. Tom is a man of high integrity and took us through every step in the process in a very supportive manner. For us, he was an excellent choice.
